data.description: Beautiful home and all spruced up and waiting for you! All on huge oversized fenced corner lot. Split floor plan with over sized closets. New exterior paint, new interior paint through out. New carpet in bedrooms and living room. Enjoy on the few cold days and nights your cozy living room with wood burning fireplace. Huge fenced in yard with barn style shed. NO hoa bring your toys! Vaulted ceilings, new light fixtures and ceiling fans. Freshly landscaped.
